      public Event(String name, String date, String organizer, Integer attendanceLimit, String description, String poster)
      Creates a new Event object with specified details.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the event.
      date - The date the event occurs (consider a proper Date object).
      organizer - The name of the event organizer.
      attendanceLimit - The maximum number of allowed attendees.
      description - A description of the event.
      poster - A poster image associated with the event.
